<hr local-id=3D"bb9310089e40">
<h2 local-id=3D"8b455f073d67" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-2.EscopoFuncionaldaListagem">2. Escopo Funcional da Listagem</=
h2>
<p local-id=3D"19527de605e4">A tela deve permitir:</p>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"dcb839736f58">
<li local-id=3D"6142b0ad232f">
<p local-id=3D"db6a3c907baa"><strong>Visualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3o de Planos</stro=
ng></p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"e5ffaea59ca4">Exibir uma lista de planos estrat=C3=A9gicos c=
ontendo, no m=C3=ADnimo:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"996534b1ce22">
<li local-id=3D"e740e919-5292-49f8-9162-a24ff5bdf7b4">
<p local-id=3D"4235eda3b248">Nome do plano</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b61d3fa3-db74-41b5-8077-b02eb2f08c97">
<p local-id=3D"c99e28f1505a">Tipo (Estrat=C3=A9gico / Gerencial)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5563f3f9-7c4b-4284-9eea-49e354e02acc">
<p local-id=3D"528426767e60">=C3=81rea</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c4def1278a94">
<p local-id=3D"2e043d28f505">Status (Publicado / N=C3=A3o publicado)<br></p=
></li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"2" local-id=3D"0bacfd073d34">
<li local-id=3D"a553ec00cccb">
<p local-id=3D"4961be190b80"><strong> Disponibilizar mecanismos de filtrage=
m por:</strong></p></li>
</ol>
<ul local-id=3D"8037195fa107">
<li local-id=3D"0b63446c-f199-4940-830e-9db8ebbb96ba">
<p local-id=3D"1014af612a93">Nome (busca textual)</p>
<ul local-id=3D"678e41b8-8494-44ad-9bba-cd6d8b51ccb6">
<li local-id=3D"90cd6255-cae5-4014-9764-b7dd88ed0da8">
<p local-id=3D"215831cb8eed">Tipo</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c1b12224-086d-420d-9737-624548c0806c">
<p local-id=3D"7703ee79c2fc">=C3=81rea</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6de9eee9-724a-4679-bfc5-6b57614c7099">
<p local-id=3D"8d39683b5092">Status<br></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"3" local-id=3D"10edcf543efe">
<li local-id=3D"198abe1a7053">
<p local-id=3D"84dce8946040"><strong>A=C3=A7=C3=B5es sobre os Planos</stron=
g></p></li>
</ol>
<p local-id=3D"dd3ecd03628b">Permitir a execu=C3=A7=C3=A3o das principais a=
=C3=A7=C3=B5es:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"92619be5-b9f4-409a-a2b0-e6361a483431">
<li local-id=3D"13390583-036f-454b-8e35-8c1ce148effa">
