<hr local-id=3D"35e3324e-379b-4775-93ea-fa206fade5ed">
<h3 local-id=3D"ff5ff7d4e7ea" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-5.3RegrasdeNeg=C3=B3cioAssociadas">5.3 Regras de Neg=C3=B3cio =
Associadas</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"95ba51e6-7461-4bd3-9a84-940fc171fe08">
<li local-id=3D"5ad620f5-1f28-4206-92e5-5e140f804e12">
<p local-id=3D"2cd6c170b189"><strong>Permiss=C3=B5es de Acesso:</strong> Es=
te bot=C3=A3o deve estar vis=C3=ADvel apenas para usu=C3=A1rios com perfil =
de <strong>Administrador</strong> ou <strong>Gestor Estrat=C3=A9gico</stron=
g>. Usu=C3=A1rios com permiss=C3=A3o apenas de leitura n=C3=A3o devem visua=
lizar ou interagir com essa op=C3=A7=C3=A3o para evitar altera=C3=A7=C3=B5e=
s indevidas nos per=C3=ADodos do plano.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"af6bcb06-af5a-4bd0-9703-8b2de77abe37">
<p local-id=3D"ee6a84681409"><strong>Contexto Visual:</strong> Ao fechar o =
modal aberto por este bot=C3=A3o, se o usu=C3=A1rio tiver exclu=C3=ADdo o c=
iclo que estava selecionado no "Select" ao lado (ex: 2=C2=BA Semestre 2024)=
, o sistema deve atualizar automaticamente a visualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3o do Canv=
as para o ciclo remanescente mais recente.</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ac58cf522fd0"></p>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro confluence-information-macro-inf=
ormation">
<span class=3D"aui-icon aui-icon-small aui-iconfont-info confluence-informa=
tion-macro-icon"></span>
<div class=3D"confluence-information-macro-body">
<p local-id=3D"f58240a66877"><strong>ATEN=C3=87=C3=83O:</strong> =C3=A9 imp=
ortante notar que o bot=C3=A3o <strong>"Ciclos"</strong> (gerenciamento) tr=
abalha em conjunto com o dropdown <strong>"Ciclo:"</strong> =C3=A0 sua dire=
ita:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"6738d3ab916e">
<li local-id=3D"ef92d205da69">
<p local-id=3D"f8a6dcd8e49b"><strong>Bot=C3=A3o "Ciclos":</strong> Configur=
a a estrutura (quais ciclos existem).</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b33095c5851a">
<p local-id=3D"fd626f36e039"><strong>Dropdown "Ciclo:":</strong> Filtra a v=
isualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3o (qual ciclo estou vendo agora) e permite alterar para=
 outros ciclos existentes.</p></li>
</ul>
</div>
</div>
<hr local-id=3D"d39d5b53637c">
<h2 local-id=3D"956e6f600b52" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-6.Perspectivas">6. Perspectivas</h2>
<h3 local-id=3D"34cb6bbb92a4" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-=E2=9E=A4Comportamento:">=E2=9E=A4 Comportamento:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"e7ff1d6c-7099-48a0-a542-45f7fb01b3ff">
<li local-id=3D"d36b7e6a-a86b-436b-a2b3-b8cbd4193f85">
<p local-id=3D"d3a4892f0140">Cada perspectiva =C3=A9 exibida como uma faixa=
/se=C3=A7=C3=A3o horizontal</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d1d989f9-3ee3-4258-a5f2-dd455f2e396a">
<p local-id=3D"0aaa46439766">Exemplo:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"4a59c45e-5192-4f4d-a842-e639aeb80a0b">
<li local-id=3D"cb6acad8-b0d5-4569-861f-d151296cd799">
<p local-id=3D"035d1c248596">Financeira</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"021bae9c-d465-4650-a3a0-bc7b71cb8ef7">
<p local-id=3D"cd27ff199e4a">Clientes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"703cbfd8-a64b-4ac3-b8a9-6b38d10530b9">
<p local-id=3D"54ab612d1891">Processos Internos</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"a4d32231-ac2f-4629-ba72-f0cc3ca460b0">
<p local-id=3D"ef51968d744e">Aprendizado &amp; Crescimento</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"b62a20faf830" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-=E2=9E=A4Funcionalidades:">=E2=9E=A4 Funcionalidades:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"f1eb5905-f0e4-4446-9595-21611b9ade18">
<li local-id=3D"90611b09-47c2-404b-b172-ff817498cb43">
<p local-id=3D"9baf9da74268">Criar nova perspectiva</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"247dce0a-db25-45f4-bc6b-72c9314cc326">
<p local-id=3D"ccc874114e07">Editar nome</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0a431c32-6c57-4e52-9988-1921226ab3bc">
<p local-id=3D"1a0ef66f1c44">Reordenar posi=C3=A7=C3=A3o (Conf. Canvas)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"76fe072c0500">
<p local-id=3D"351c385d6da6">Op=C3=A7=C3=A3o de Remover</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6951ba43-67a5-42b5-9890-c44ac405872f">
<p local-id=3D"07e6dcf1f491">Exibi=C3=A7=C3=A3o de quantidade de objetivos =
associados (ex: =E2=80=9C3 obj=E2=80=9D)</p></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"4e4b2dd6-66d5-4a45-9205-666211cba495">
<h2 local-id=3D"cad27df4087e" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-7.ObjetivosEstrat=C3=A9gicos(Cards)">7. Objetivos Estrat=C3=A9=
gicos (Cards)</h2>
<p local-id=3D"cd618943a1c5">Cada objetivo ser=C3=A1 exibido como um card d=
entro da perspectiva.</p>
<h3 local-id=3D"e2dd808032ba" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-7.1EstruturadoCard:">7.1 Estrutura do Card:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"f83b0234-ec96-417f-8a3a-60e484eb0845">
<li local-id=3D"9b6663f9-3fe8-4102-b804-6a6c635b9ad6">
<p local-id=3D"3c295c6a6542">C=C3=B3digo (ex: FIN-01)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"189a18be-7335-4ab5-8730-570326ee74be">
<p local-id=3D"86c1c7c3311c">Nome do objetivo</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0b284d05-6b3d-43bf-a222-160611277d80">
<p local-id=3D"0390a993a827">Percentual de progresso</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"06d1cfcf-61a7-4cdf-a036-831cb9f8323b">
<p local-id=3D"4f00e6b8f7ea">Barra de progresso</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"cfc226bb-dc8f-446b-9d06-2ce42a896186">
<p local-id=3D"9760aa0b2518">=C3=8Dcones de apoio:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e1af5d8d-1329-4e93-a3cc-61981db6bffc">
<li local-id=3D"52b525e8-d98a-464d-ae4d-f8bddd30cf67">
<p local-id=3D"9e9276dd2189">Rela=C3=A7=C3=B5es</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"008098ec-c15b-4425-99e2-6720aa77a7f8">
<p local-id=3D"bc3e7abdda17">Indicadores</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"bc7a876b-fdce-45a7-b431-527a8f145351">
<p local-id=3D"f443e4cf0433">Iniciativas</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<hr local-id=3D"d61801cb-0261-447f-9825-3067771b6617">
<h3 local-id=3D"ae57508107ec" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-7.2RegrasdeNeg=C3=B3cio:">7.2 Regras de Neg=C3=B3cio:</h3>
<h4 local-id=3D"e218834c514f" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-=E2=9C=94Progresso:">=E2=9C=94 Progresso:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"b3dbcf29-8336-4054-ba26-5007a1b4a928">
<li local-id=3D"57436611-0838-4b24-9438-b6f6c85573a4">
<p local-id=3D"ec7fa488f45a">Calculado automaticamente (com base em indicad=
ores e KRs )</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ba57ef56-11da-44b4-b471-1ba1b58f0a52">
<p local-id=3D"d338a62b7823">Exibido em % + barra visual</p></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"79dc79312bec" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-=E2=9C=94Cores:">=E2=9C=94 Cores:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"07af9446-b1e1-41a8-9e88-0ff4e88dbc4e">
<li local-id=3D"41c09dc2-c7a6-4d2b-9e81-20599fd7f85a">
<p local-id=3D"2557dd44a6fb">Vermelho =E2=86=92 atraso / baixo desempenho</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"5d9bb80d-025c-4a0e-88a2-c72da0478eb8">
<p local-id=3D"ad526a3828c6">Amarelo =E2=86=92 aten=C3=A7=C3=A3o</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"de09a90e-2728-4c1f-85a4-e9b4aa03fc99">
<p local-id=3D"9ba6e4e7482b">Verde =E2=86=92 dentro do esperado</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e6d5c07f9304">
<li local-id=3D"26cea5ba5727">
<p local-id=3D"978c730c9b9d">Obs: Conforme o esquema de cores do Plano Estr=
at=C3=A9gico</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<h4 local-id=3D"1ba9e92b38d6" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-=E2=9C=94Intera=C3=A7=C3=B5es:">=E2=9C=94 Intera=C3=A7=C3=B5es=
:</h4>
<ul local-id=3D"5db6825a735a">
<li local-id=3D"b3f8032e-3a88-42e8-8b69-8902bd340008">
<p local-id=3D"b09d80ae40f1">Clique no card do Objetivo abre o detalhe (Dra=
wer)</p></li>
</ul>
<ol start=3D"1" local-id=3D"424f945ee85b">
<li local-id=3D"2d4f0b0a0a19">
<p local-id=3D"04fbc08e3b38">Aba KRs: Listagem de Krs com valores Cadastro =
de KRs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3a91391b7921">
<p local-id=3D"643f4ae2d404">Aba Associar Plano de A=C3=A7=C3=A3o (inclusiv=
e a correla=C3=A7=C3=A3o dos Planos)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ff802b23c056">
<p local-id=3D"627af6078579">Criar Grupos de Plano de A=C3=A7=C3=A3o</p></l=
i>
<li local-id=3D"332eec2e29c6">
<p local-id=3D"7538dcb050ed">Criar Riscos</p></li>
</ol>
<hr local-id=3D"02d8c899c8c2">
<h2 local-id=3D"6ff527fa96e4" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-8.RelacionamentodoObjetivocomProjetos,Programas,Iniciativas,KR=
s,Indicadores,PlanosdeA=C3=A7=C3=B5es,GruposdeA=C3=A7=C3=B5eseRiscos.">8. R=
elacionamento do Objetivo com Projetos, Programas, Iniciativas, KRs, Indica=
dores, Planos de A=C3=A7=C3=B5es, Grupos de A=C3=A7=C3=B5es e Riscos.</h2>
<p local-id=3D"bc3b73600782">Na tela atual da Plataforma, ao acessar um Obj=
etivo Estrat=C3=A9gico, existe a funcionalidade de associa=C3=A7=C3=A3o com=
 os seguintes elementos: Projetos, Programas, Iniciativas, Planos de A=C3=
=A7=C3=B5es e Grupos de A=C3=A7=C3=B5es.</p>
<p local-id=3D"a898cb86fd4c">Para o novo layout, o <strong>DRAWER de associ=
a=C3=A7=C3=B5es</strong> dever=C3=A1 ser evolu=C3=ADdo para contemplar tamb=
=C3=A9m os seguintes itens adicionais:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"954f0e3a-04bf-4c08-93fd-3a2820f6bdb8">
<li local-id=3D"0d00de2e-4f96-41ef-8849-381d5de52ba7">
<p local-id=3D"a6ae2724bb8d"><strong>KRs (Key Results)</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"891de381-bfc2-4871-99b6-f16b6baa0c7b">
<p local-id=3D"c303f3713088"><strong>Riscos</strong></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"02cac7ac6f77">Dessa forma, o DRAWER passar=C3=A1 a permitir =
a associa=C3=A7=C3=A3o com:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"24567f0a-efcc-434d-9959-f9fbf3a43ac8">
<li local-id=3D"2020df19-030a-4a4b-a840-b160163bf323">
<p local-id=3D"68f6cda5dc4f">Projetos</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"30aa1b20-61fb-463c-bc9a-60ca34dcbbc3">
<p local-id=3D"62eee07153f7">Programas</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1d615b7d-503a-49a7-bf47-fd343bc1171c">
<p local-id=3D"87f4e29c486f">Iniciativas</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c62a91ff-ce5c-44fa-b449-187236d5e649">
<p local-id=3D"76852b909037">KRs</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d3093177034f">
<p local-id=3D"716926e86f2b">Indicadores</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"de5d92bd-a2e0-453f-9dbf-2a68f3c42f89">
<p local-id=3D"93825f536f7c">Planos de A=C3=A7=C3=B5es</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"69edf9e2-7193-4a69-b766-a80a2b16ed4c">
<p local-id=3D"39912eaf04f4">Grupos de A=C3=A7=C3=B5es</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"59b78950-b1fe-40c5-b6b4-00c9a0250ca5">
<p local-id=3D"517bc755ff25">Riscos</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"76a4d26c60be">A navega=C3=A7=C3=A3o dentro do DRAWER dever=
=C3=A1 ser organizada por abas, permitindo ao usu=C3=A1rio alternar facilme=
nte entre os diferentes tipos de associa=C3=A7=C3=A3o.<br></p>
<hr local-id=3D"0e8ae4c5f82e">
<p local-id=3D"1a36a948e86e"><strong>8.1 Aba KRs</strong><br><br><strong>Ob=
jetivo:</strong> Permitir o cadastro, acompanhamento e gest=C3=A3o de <stro=
ng>Resultados-Chave (KRs)</strong> vinculados a um Objetivo Estrat=C3=A9gic=
o, com foco em mensura=C3=A7=C3=A3o de progresso.<br><br><strong>Contexto d=
e uso</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"6c3e01ecc85c">Dentro do objetivo (ex: <em>Elevar NPS do Clie=
nte</em>), o usu=C3=A1rio pode:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b0d92aa6-1ad4-470e-8311-b3cabc9b6283">
<li local-id=3D"9e4e48e5-f712-4080-bddb-908ecfc3fcc0">
<p local-id=3D"06ac46224f56">Visualizar KRs existentes</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"13b43eb4-e0b7-46e8-9281-bed1be62de9a">
<p local-id=3D"915cf7d6bded">Acompanhar progresso (%)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"43487107-4e41-4e07-af1a-cbd8fc320f19">
<p local-id=3D"90efbd3bc7ef">Criar novos KRs via <strong>mini formul=C3=A1r=
io inline</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"48872455-c380-4e62-98e0-457115cb1730">
<p local-id=3D"0e829bf57deb">+ Registrar medi=C3=A7=C3=B5es</p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5a9ddebcd4c5">=E2=9E=A4 <strong>Componentes da Tela</strong>=
 (Listagem de KRs)</p>
<p local-id=3D"772d21cedecf">Cada KR deve ser exibido em formato de card co=
ntendo:</p>
<p local-id=3D"79482c633ddd">=E2=9E=A4 <strong>Campos exibidos:</strong></p=
>
<ul local-id=3D"b4eb1e85-b1a0-4313-9b41-89d4abff8628">
<li local-id=3D"05c8367a-ea02-4e9f-b14b-9a1b71e6dc96">
<p local-id=3D"1502ecbe68f4">Nome do KR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f58e39da-2327-46a6-86d9-36887a996b5a">
<p local-id=3D"2cbebb3ab42e">Barra de progresso (%)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"08c78298-af9e-4d09-b32c-0020a6df0441">
<p local-id=3D"7ff620a5dad6">Percentual consolidado (ex: 70%)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c96defa-4c20-4383-9bb8-8747ac9d5a88">
<p local-id=3D"ff0ad6fc40d9">Indicador visual de tend=C3=AAncia (=F0=9F=93=
=88 / =F0=9F=93=89)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"8cc14ca0-bbeb-4724-ae93-b521bf672026">
<p local-id=3D"cb64c0c643ca">Dados num=C3=A9ricos:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"52179465-55dc-41ea-ae67-824ac2741a8d">
<li local-id=3D"1793ce02-9bba-4c24-9406-c4f1db8c3b2c">
<p local-id=3D"10d6c4a56fcb"><strong>Baseline</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2a1409e0-a1bf-43d9-b490-2eb16fdd6866">
<p local-id=3D"5cf5915154d0"><strong>Meta</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"3622b3d1-b968-4779-bc74-9706b86d0c0c">
<p local-id=3D"7b5e4693dedb"><strong>Atual</strong><br></p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"eacdabdf628f">=E2=9E=A4<strong> Adicionar Resultado-Chave (M=
ini Formul=C3=A1rio Inline)</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"eb924c35bb56"><strong>A=C3=A7=C3=A3o: </strong>Ao clicar em =
<strong>=E2=80=9C+ Adicionar Resultado-Chave=E2=80=9D</strong>, deve abrir =
um formul=C3=A1rio inline (expandido na pr=C3=B3pria tela) =E2=80=94 n=C3=
=A3o modal.<br><br>
=E2=9E=A4 Campos do Fomul=C3=A1rio Inline</p>
<ul local-id=3D"12bcf270-d8e2-4d31-b1a6-71c1f3adecd8">
<li local-id=3D"52f3f884-4d9b-4883-9078-cb4eae708d50">
<p local-id=3D"178b316fa421"><strong>Nome do KR</strong>* (texto)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4373a1ba-805c-493a-9f84-b73015db3c95">
<p local-id=3D"7505d3dddde2"><strong>Baseline</strong> (num=C3=A9rico)</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"060848a2-2ab6-4b3e-bb09-c2f117936ed4">
<p local-id=3D"42937c92a509"><strong>Meta</strong> (num=C3=A9rico)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7570fd7d-76d7-4797-8aae-66fc2ffaa76c">
<p local-id=3D"adccaec79c5d"><strong>Unidade</strong> (texto curto ou dropd=
own)</p>
<ul local-id=3D"3ea1e633-f03d-4777-8e85-6667d06870ad">
<li local-id=3D"0923e826-9834-4d51-9154-b92105b4dec9">
<p local-id=3D"084e9f8395c9">Ex: %, pontos, R$, quantidade</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"fa87477b-a93a-4885-9585-978cb2ee87f3">
<p local-id=3D"1e33f5831fe3"><strong>Dire=C3=A7=C3=A3o do indicador</strong=
> (dropdown):</p>
<ul local-id=3D"231cb768-4778-47f3-a11e-542fe6e17507">
<li local-id=3D"8a24161d-b968-464f-b16f-ef40af07cc59">
<p local-id=3D"ac1674038e5b">Maior =C3=A9 melhor</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"55b610a9-9727-4fcf-8fb3-7a7a6bda705f">
<p local-id=3D"f61af4cae30f">Menor =C3=A9 melhor</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"52e9fe9c9e7b">=E2=9E=A4 <strong>Edi=C3=A7=C3=A3o do KRs</str=
ong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ca169d91-979c-4765-a43c-fec87a04000a">
<li local-id=3D"e14461e0-f523-4cf9-a871-1c57a8cc0870">
<p local-id=3D"efca934e0e9a">Clique no card do Kr e poder editar ou icone d=
e l=C3=A1pis para edi=C3=A7=C3=A3o</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"85ef265b-b702-4cc8-8c5d-637d05b26621">
<p local-id=3D"2afd078618ac">Campos edit=C3=A1veis:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"63171312338c">
<li local-id=3D"d8a3933a75c1">
<p local-id=3D"ed978d50112c">Nome do KR</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4092701f-20b8-4da9-851a-d69b43997a59">
<p local-id=3D"36bdfb35c6d3">Atual</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"c5a96de1-d8aa-4c25-ade5-997b04b99b6f">
<p local-id=3D"945331e76a3b">Meta</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
