<hr local-id=3D"1d519872ed69">
<p local-id=3D"3908d744cf03"><strong>8.3 Aba Riscos</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"a80e4280a2c0"><strong>Objetivo:</strong> Permitir o cadastro=
, visualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3o e gest=C3=A3o de riscos associados a um <strong>Ob=
jetivo Estrat=C3=A9gico</strong>, incluindo classifica=C3=A7=C3=A3o, impact=
o, probabilidade, respons=C3=A1vel e a=C3=A7=C3=B5es de mitiga=C3=A7=C3=A3o=
.<br><br>
Contexto de uso</p>
<ul local-id=3D"b3ad9d953d38">
<li local-id=3D"7a2d13a2-f000-4d42-bf32-776a64534f97">
<p local-id=3D"91601193023f">A aba <strong>Riscos</strong> =C3=A9 acessada =
dentro do detalhe de um objetivo (ex: <em>Elevar NPS do Cliente</em>).</p><=
/li>
<li local-id=3D"b84296eb-1c02-4b63-89dd-4b4346b9e438">
<p local-id=3D"b9a45ba77f5d">O usu=C3=A1rio pode:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"2e6cb9f2-ae58-4240-acd4-24b7705e5c7d">
<li local-id=3D"5fa88dad-2973-44e8-8f61-714968b7a960">
<p local-id=3D"9bb534cd43f8">Visualizar riscos j=C3=A1 cadastrados</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"2bde5982-af1a-4fc0-9edb-1e0eac302b18">
<p local-id=3D"217389032acd">Criar novos riscos</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"901fd934-5a61-4fd5-85d9-62f98f27337f">
<p local-id=3D"3cad368779cf">Atualizar status e informa=C3=A7=C3=B5es<br></=
p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"ea2d0f2ae271"><strong>Componentes da Tela</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"f9f3b1a7557b"><strong>Listagem de Riscos</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"627978163fa6">Cada risco deve ser exibido em formato de card=
 contendo:</p>
<p local-id=3D"610e56f0875c"><strong>Campos exibidos:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"7f6fa9fb-f383-41a0-8e81-59c32165960a">
<li local-id=3D"cd6d7b68-8460-4077-a9d2-998ba58f99cb">
<p local-id=3D"50aeef6c6a5e">=F0=9F=94=B4 Indicador visual de severidade (c=
or)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dc84acb6-d49a-470f-80bc-d25a08bf680f">
<p local-id=3D"f4616f6d0134"><strong>Nome do risco</strong></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"f647d6f6-9122-442c-a03e-7834c791b982">
<p local-id=3D"b46f5225f685"><strong>Descri=C3=A7=C3=A3o resumida</strong><=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"dfeb690e-4f61-4b5f-bfae-de3a6b67ff5b">
<p local-id=3D"0f2806322817"><strong>Tags/Classifica=C3=A7=C3=B5es:</strong=
></p>
<ul local-id=3D"ab40a703-4b3e-4b17-bb82-0fb608707eb0">
<li local-id=3D"15b58f76-8691-4ae6-85e0-ceedc5f1d45b">
<p local-id=3D"48fbad14bc1d">Tipo (ex: Estrat=C3=A9gico, Operacional)</p></=
li>
<li local-id=3D"e8bf64c6-c6f6-4709-a8ee-054bea9fb5ba">
<p local-id=3D"f6b797d5d540">Probabilidade (P: Baixa, M=C3=A9dia, Alta)</p>=
</li>
<li local-id=3D"0861584e-242f-4623-b522-caa3ef5ca574">
<p local-id=3D"fd2ad288a492">Impacto (I: Baixo, M=C3=A9dio, Alto)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"e4fc5c1a-ebc3-4b5c-8cfa-6e7689d74875">
<p local-id=3D"e6e17718f5ab">Criticidade (calculada automaticamente)</p></l=
i>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"7e5fe14c-0287-4d82-9522-50037ad5d33b">
<p local-id=3D"d9d08874dd78"><strong>Mitiga=C3=A7=C3=A3o (resumo)</strong><=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1212520b-0abf-4af5-83a2-765bb0f3ed8c">
<p local-id=3D"ee5dfe2817b5"><strong>Respons=C3=A1vel (ex: CS Lead)</strong=
></p></li>
<li local-id=3D"fda3bef0-2859-4537-b732-32623f6a8c9c">
<p local-id=3D"21825149f1c4"><strong>Status (dropdown):</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"50f4f8b4-1e88-4500-93ab-bd1bbb4a5f66">
<li local-id=3D"e28adf5c-b587-418d-afa3-cfad367918fa">
<p local-id=3D"9598fae4d802">Identificado</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"80bcc8e9-4268-4b53-ba7f-dabec6b3eb18">
<p local-id=3D"b21019ce14e6">Em mitiga=C3=A7=C3=A3o</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"25a5c8ca-8fbe-40e2-b526-75ad0a543c41">
<p local-id=3D"17fe59839f12">Mitigado</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"62db73c8-05b6-49ad-b669-689c88e7bf6a">
<p local-id=3D"a021d4212d36">Aceito</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"384e0f8d9e54">=E2=9E=A4 <strong>Adicionar Novo Risco (Formul=
=C3=A1rio)</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"f15fe5ee55cc"><strong>Campos obrigat=C3=B3rios:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"f222ccd4-5fbe-41cb-b8a6-040436695822">
<li local-id=3D"14c71b7b-7743-4f0b-a4e1-814d4e68f5ca">
<p local-id=3D"18f47b8637ef"><strong>Nome do risco</strong>* (input texto)<=
/p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0550609e-94bd-4d85-85e4-601a27b6923a">
<p local-id=3D"b57821d2755c"><strong>Descri=C3=A7=C3=A3o</strong> (texto)</=
p></li>
<li local-id=3D"ae5b1980-3fb4-4bb1-8904-b8f177f9a183">
<p local-id=3D"1b5167cf8998"><strong>Tipo</strong> (dropdown)</p>
<ul local-id=3D"73363a51-4a88-4b51-83c4-a963611f3773">
<li local-id=3D"2a1a0f84-5740-4c65-aca0-677769fa3aa7">
<p local-id=3D"6c6d8efd5a68">Operacional</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"1da69655-034d-4eb6-b799-c6e3987bcc00">
<p local-id=3D"243324aff09e">Financeiro</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b279f726-fa7a-4647-8b75-59fc0f90b6b2">
<p local-id=3D"c0ee415bd532">Estrat=C3=A9gico</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"0ac9b9a4-a3f3-49a1-9764-352c181c1a73">
<p local-id=3D"c7c436490793">Regulat=C3=B3rio</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"6c1fde12-cc0b-4f8e-9275-ebd502214385">
<p local-id=3D"386806d72435">Tecnol=C3=B3gico</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4d1028ee-16d4-4550-b87c-7d54838e66b5">
<p local-id=3D"2ca48f4dede7">Pessoas</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"e8fcda86-cdbd-460a-891b-e611c24e6693">
<p local-id=3D"92801d34d54a"><strong>Probabilidade (P)</strong> (dropdown)<=
/p>
<ul local-id=3D"8d606187-09c6-46b9-8b8b-6df98f146fa4">
<li local-id=3D"d4297385-693b-4634-b852-c703cbdc8957">
<p local-id=3D"9701bc33bf56">Baixa / M=C3=A9dia / Alta</p></li>
</ul></li>
<li local-id=3D"6959f86d-e717-451c-88a7-d33a2c0d0626">
<p local-id=3D"ef205763b29d"><strong>Impacto (I)</strong> (dropdown)</p>
<ul local-id=3D"ed71014b-b978-42cf-a156-4957532a2465">
<li local-id=3D"43e32011-a041-4614-a3b5-b9e933ed85fa">
<p local-id=3D"3aab05218f00">Baixo / M=C3=A9dio / Alto</p></li>
</ul></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"561c59941a10"><strong>Campos opcionais:</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"9b1fd4a4-3e82-4aee-89ff-35b6306b6082">
<li local-id=3D"f11e7ffe-11cd-4cd9-97b6-b50033dd951b">
<p local-id=3D"0ffb2315e4cc"><strong>A=C3=A7=C3=A3o de mitiga=C3=A7=C3=A3o<=
/strong> (texto)</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"7e0b0434-f527-43cc-b59b-3cd0b87e97bf">
<p local-id=3D"d48f42977b17"><strong>Respons=C3=A1vel</strong> (autocomplet=
e / sele=C3=A7=C3=A3o de usu=C3=A1rio)</p></li>
</ul>
