o(BSCCanvas)-Tipos:">Tipos:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"4187f28d-444f-4eec-b589-4bdf721a6664">
<li local-id=3D"0a797c2b-8626-4cb4-8249-127218815a90">
<p local-id=3D"46bb7f205f3e">Rela=C3=A7=C3=A3o de causa e efeito</p></li>
</ul>
