o(BSCCanvas)-Comportamento:">Comportamento:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"2c46883f-9648-4a61-b3f7-47b4a0054161">
<li local-id=3D"ac9ecc6e-41b0-46d0-b962-f9ffa087ad51">
<p local-id=3D"d279bf39c80e">Representadas por setas entre os cards</p></li=
>
</ul>
<h3 local-id=3D"bcb9f99636a1" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-Funcionalidades:">Funcionalidades:</h3>
<ul local-id=3D"d8b99095-995a-4343-a823-c21005b07e0e">
<li local-id=3D"1ff49eb4-27e5-44d6-a507-5100446401ee">
<p local-id=3D"d98f071113fa">Criar rela=C3=A7=C3=A3o manual (bot=C3=A3o =E2=
=80=9CAdicionar rela=C3=A7=C3=A3o=E2=80=9D)</p></li>
