<hr local-id=3D"8fffcd42-4968-4f4c-adf5-0cd395458674">
<h2 local-id=3D"45367492cba4" id=3D"Release2-NovaTeladePlanoEstrat=C3=A9gic=
o(BSCCanvas)-10.ConfigurarCanvas">10. Configurar Canvas</h2>
<p local-id=3D"b1142fc904f6">Ao clicar no bot=C3=A3o <strong>=E2=80=9CConfi=
gurar Canvas=E2=80=9D</strong>, o sistema deve abrir um modal central conte=
ndo as configura=C3=A7=C3=B5es de layout e perspectivas do mapa estrat=C3=
=A9gico.<br><br><strong>Abas de Navega=C3=A7=C3=A3o:</strong> O modal =C3=
=A9 dividido em duas partes: <strong>Perspectivas</strong> (ajustes de core=
s) e <strong>Layout</strong> (que cuida do posicionamento visual).</p><span=
 class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-=
embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image image-center"=
 alt=3D"image-20260331-144021.png" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"b7=
29edf72d971eff61b29844a66fb82523fe40a8ba080731d9f9aff15e449038" data-image-=
src=3D"https://channel.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/4133945351/i=
mage-20260331-144021.png?version=3D1&amp;modificationDate=3D1774968026203&a=
mp;cacheVersion=3D1&amp;api=3Dv2" data-height=3D"845" data-width=3D"1638" d=
ata-unresolved-comment-count=3D"0" data-linked-resource-id=3D"4135157763" d=
ata-linked-resource-version=3D"1" data-linked-resource-type=3D"attachment" =
data-linked-resource-default-alias=3D"image-20260331-144021.png" data-base-=
url=3D"https://channel.atlassian.net/wiki" data-linked-resource-content-typ=
e=3D"image/png" data-linked-resource-container-id=3D"4133945351" data-linke=
d-resource-container-version=3D"31" data-media-id=3D"f7d3c73b-b74f-47da-b7d=
b-1038ce811a9e" data-media-type=3D"file" height=3D"241"></span>
<p local-id=3D"ba4f6c8b23e3"><br></p>
<p local-id=3D"62079c5989c0"><strong>=3D&gt; Presets R=C3=A1pidos (Configur=
a=C3=A7=C3=B5es Pr=C3=A9-definidas)</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"81610852736f">Esta se=C3=A7=C3=A3o permite ao usu=C3=A1rio e=
scolher modelos de organiza=C3=A7=C3=A3o autom=C3=A1tica com um clique:</p>
<ul local-id=3D"e9e5a35d-1597-445d-a408-13b52f1c27b5">
<li local-id=3D"3b43af55-23d2-48db-b0f3-5ebabc07532e">
<p local-id=3D"f7f5eb14bfbf"><strong>Todas empilhadas:</strong> As perspect=
ivas ficam uma abaixo da outra, ocupando toda a largura.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"eccf97b6-0109-41c4-8742-40850d13d7a0">
<p local-id=3D"50b2e1e27fdb"><strong>2 colunas (=C3=BAltimo empilhado):</st=
rong> Cria duas colunas laterais, mas mant=C3=A9m o =C3=BAltimo item ocupan=
do a largura total.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"b035b1b7-2de1-4900-995a-0487a1c005d7">
<p local-id=3D"e0664b5a54c6"><strong>3 colunas (primeira linha):</strong> O=
rganiza o topo em tr=C3=AAs colunas menores.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"d8cb336331a4">
<p local-id=3D"1cd2ea56e86a">O ajuste pode ser individual diretamente na =
=E2=80=9Ctabela=E2=80=9D de cada perpectiva de como o usu=C3=A1rio desejar.=
<br></p></li>
</ul>
<p local-id=3D"5d4361e3f481"><strong>=3D&gt; Preview layout</strong></p>
<p local-id=3D"011e115aca1f">Ao justar par=C3=A2metros como linha, coluna e=
 largura das perspectivas, o sistema atualiza automaticamente a =C3=A1rea d=
e preview, exibindo uma representa=C3=A7=C3=A3o simplificada da distribui=
=C3=A7=C3=A3o dos elementos no canvas. Essa visualiza=C3=A7=C3=A3o =C3=A9 a=
penas ilustrativa e n=C3=A3o impacta o mapa estrat=C3=A9gico ativo at=C3=A9=
 que o usu=C3=A1rio confirme a a=C3=A7=C3=A3o por meio do bot=C3=A3o <stron=
g>=E2=80=9CSalvar configura=C3=A7=C3=A3o=E2=80=9D</strong>. Caso opte por c=
ancelar ou fechar o modal, nenhuma altera=C3=A7=C3=A3o =C3=A9 aplicada.<br>=
</p>
<p local-id=3D"64dd0faf090f"><strong>=3D&gt; A=C3=A7=C3=B5es de Rodap=C3=A9=
</strong></p>
<ul local-id=3D"1eee10f3-20a8-4b11-8278-6a9baefa8487">
<li local-id=3D"b4f8b967-8b7d-4c7b-92f6-2d63c0dc67f1">
<p local-id=3D"a5a91e2482d4"><strong>Bot=C3=A3o Cancelar:</strong> Fecha o =
modal sem salvar as altera=C3=A7=C3=B5es.</p></li>
<li local-id=3D"4e0469a8-8be8-4bbe-8ee9-13fe31a193cb">
<p local-id=3D"3a3c3c9e8618"><strong>Bot=C3=A3o Salvar configura=C3=A7=C3=
=A3o:</strong> Aplica as mudan=C3=A7as de posicionamento ao mapa estrat=C3=
=A9gico principal.</p></li>
</ul><span class=3D"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper c=
onfluence-embedded-manual-size"><img class=3D"confluence-embedded-image con=
fluence-content-image-border image-center" alt=3D"image-20260407-143131.png=
" width=3D"468" loading=3D"lazy" src=3D"aad25f1b2df007202cb575dd5d7c29a777c=
